PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Rochelle Joanne BIELBY, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 159508
COA: 340556 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 10, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the March 5, 2019 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
